cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB

This paper deals with natural language generation from structured data, which is a common topic in the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL). It also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) techniques for generating textual descriptions. Additionally, the use of knowledge graphs suggests a connection to database systems (cs.DB).
